Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:26.38,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48\c&HF7F9F9&\shad2\4c&H77898D&\pos(170,585)}(ECHIKA)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说没有一个客人是为了来看我们才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也是因为我们对这个条件妥协了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能实现最速出道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.59,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48\c&HF7F9F9&\pos(1030,490)\shad2\4c&H77898D&}icy tail
