Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.59,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48\c&HF7F9F9&\pos(1030,630)\shad2\4c&H77898D&}(RANKO)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下只能靠你们自己的实力打出一片大天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚软了吗 想退场现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚软了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.53,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48\c&HF7F9F9&\pos(1140,120)\shad2\4c&H77898D&}icy tail
