Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩？惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…我叫错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…不是叫错了
